data.description: Experience a spacious 4-bedroom haven with an open layout. The 4th bedroom offers versatility as a bonus room or flex space. Panoramic sliding doors open to an inviting enclosed porch, ideal for relaxation and entertaining in the large, private yard. Located in prime Wake Forest, this home boasts granite countertops, luxury vinyl plank flooring, upgraded lighting, a screened porch, ceiling fans in every bedroom, elegant bathroom finishes, and the convenience of a tankless water heater. Your new home is waiting—visit today!
